1
00:00:12,900 --> 00:00:14,100
I never thought about

2
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:15,461
being with Young Master Yan.

3
00:00:17,021 --> 00:00:17,821
But

4
00:00:18,900 --> 00:00:20,540
why are you so good to me?

5
00:00:22,461 --> 00:00:23,861
I told you before,

6
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:25,260
don't think too much

7
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:26,380
or ask too many questions.

8
00:00:26,380 --> 00:00:27,461
It's not good for us

9
00:00:27,461 --> 00:00:29,021
to think too much or ask too many questions.

10
00:00:29,181 --> 00:00:30,901
You should think about

11
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:33,261
your future now.

12
00:00:39,301 --> 00:00:40,100
Alright, Mr. Gu.

13
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:42,460
I appreciate your kindness.

14
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:45,261
I know what I should and shouldn't do.

15
00:00:45,420 --> 00:00:46,301
I'm clear on that.

16
00:00:47,261 --> 00:00:48,060
Don't worry.

17
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,261
Hearing you say that,

18
00:00:51,140 --> 00:00:51,981
I'm relieved.

19
00:00:54,701 --> 00:00:55,420
Xiaoxue,

20
00:00:56,661 --> 00:00:57,941
if you ever need anything in the future,

21
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:00,420
just come to me.

22
00:01:04,621 --> 00:01:07,580
Auntie, you don't look well.

23
00:01:07,741 --> 00:01:09,101
Why don't you go to our beauty salon?

24
00:01:09,101 --> 00:01:10,901
I'll ask them to give you a good treatment.

25
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:13,541
I just came back,

26
00:01:14,101 --> 00:01:15,621
seeing the weeds all over the yard,

27
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:17,020
I felt uncomfortable.

28
00:01:17,901 --> 00:01:19,341
These weeds

29
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:21,140
are not only unsightly,

30
00:01:21,981 --> 00:01:23,621
but also absorb the nutrients of flowers.

31
00:01:24,981 --> 00:01:27,500
Auntie, weeds are weeds after all.

32
00:01:28,060 --> 00:01:30,500
They will keep draining

33
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,741
the flowers' nutrients.

34
00:01:31,860 --> 00:01:33,101
It's really annoying.

35
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:34,381
Are you talking about...

36
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:37,101
I'm talking about these flowers.

37
00:01:40,780 --> 00:01:42,780
The flowers and grass in the Gu Family

38
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,020
should be trimmed.

39
00:01:50,140 --> 00:01:51,341
Do you know

40
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:53,381
how long it took me to make you

41
00:01:53,381 --> 00:01:54,500
the successor of the Gu Group?

42
00:01:54,981 --> 00:01:56,101
You're not worried at all.

43
00:01:58,261 --> 00:02:00,181
I've got everything in order internally.

44
00:02:01,181 --> 00:02:02,981
Many shareholders support you.

45
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:04,860
Next,

46
00:02:05,101 --> 00:02:07,941
you should attend more management meetings.

47
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:10,381
The key is

48
00:02:11,381 --> 00:02:13,580
to marry Wanqing

49
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,860
as soon as possible.

50
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:18,381
Only then can you outshine Gu Chengyan.

51
00:02:19,381 --> 00:02:21,180
Don't underestimate her.

52
00:02:21,981 --> 00:02:24,061
We're not sure

53
00:02:24,061 --> 00:02:25,340
if she'll really give up Chengyan.

54
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:28,180
Your priority is to marry her

55
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:29,701
and keep a tight grip on her.

56
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:32,420
I see.

57
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,381
That Ji Xiaoxue

58
00:02:36,781 --> 00:02:37,740
is your doing, right?

59
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:40,900
She's not simple.

60
00:02:41,781 --> 00:02:44,340
Gu Chengyan seems to be fond of her.

61
00:02:44,941 --> 00:02:45,860
Don't worry.

62
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:47,941
Everything is under my control.

63
00:02:48,941 --> 00:02:51,340
Anyway, keep an eye on her.

64
00:02:58,460 --> 00:02:59,620
Anyway,

65
00:02:59,781 --> 00:03:02,221
The Gu and Xia families will marry.

66
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:04,941
There's no problem to move in early.

67
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:08,580
I moved in mainly to accompany aunt.

68
00:03:08,941 --> 00:03:10,821
If you don't want me to stay here,

69
00:03:10,941 --> 00:03:11,781
I can leave.

70
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:12,941
Xiao Qing

71
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,020
How could we not want you to stay here?

72
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:17,941
The Gu family and the Xia family have been friends for generations.

73
00:03:18,261 --> 00:03:21,381
And you are working in our company now.

74
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:23,261
We are already a family.

75
00:03:23,781 --> 00:03:24,740
We're in this together.

76
00:03:25,020 --> 00:03:26,061
Thank you, Uncle Gu.

77
00:03:27,541 --> 00:03:28,381
But

78
00:03:29,781 --> 00:03:31,221
I'm worried about my dad.

79
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:32,541
My dad agrees.

80
00:03:34,661 --> 00:03:35,300
Okay.

81
00:03:36,221 --> 00:03:37,180
Chengyan is here.

82
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:38,221
That's good.

83
00:03:38,821 --> 00:03:39,860
Wanqing

84
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:41,580
will move into our house.

85
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,180
You don't have any objections, do you?

86
00:03:44,501 --> 00:03:45,340
No.

87
00:03:45,941 --> 00:03:46,620
Good.

88
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:15,340
I was rude yesterday.

89
00:04:15,821 --> 00:04:16,861
I'm sorry.

90
00:04:16,941 --> 00:04:18,421
It's okay, Miss Xia.

91
00:04:37,821 --> 00:04:39,580
Xia Wanqing just moved in.

92
00:04:40,301 --> 00:04:41,140
You should be careful.

93
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:42,980
I don't think

94
00:04:43,701 --> 00:04:45,340
Miss Xia will do anything to me.

95
00:04:51,381 --> 00:04:52,660
You are too kind,

96
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,821
You always think others won't hurt you.

97
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:56,861
But what's the result?

98
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:58,340
But don't worry.

99
00:04:58,780 --> 00:04:59,660
She can't be too rude

100
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,020
in my family.

101
00:05:02,301 --> 00:05:03,501
The only thing I'm worried about

102
00:05:04,261 --> 00:05:05,301
is my stepmother.

103
00:05:06,261 --> 00:05:07,381
Xia Wanqing's sudden arrival

104
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:09,100
must be her idea.

105
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:10,181
Do you think

106
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:12,741
there's a chance

107
00:05:13,181 --> 00:05:14,140
between them?

108
00:05:18,381 --> 00:05:21,261
As long as you're willing to marry her,

109
00:05:21,621 --> 00:05:22,780
I believe she'll choose you.

110
00:05:24,261 --> 00:05:25,181
She likes you.

111
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:27,421
I...

112
00:05:27,421 --> 00:05:28,340
You don't have to say anything.

113
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,421
I know.

114
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:31,181
Don't worry.

115
00:05:31,501 --> 00:05:32,980
No matter what decision you make,

116
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:34,421
I'll support you.

117
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:46,301
You should take a rest at home today.

118
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:48,861
I'll meet

119
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,580
Xia Wanqing's father with Gu Chengjing

120
00:05:51,301 --> 00:05:52,621
to deal with the Su's Art Gallery.

121
00:05:53,941 --> 00:05:54,540
Okay.

122
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:06,821
Do you think

123
00:06:07,741 --> 00:06:09,100
Xia Wanqing and Gu Chengjing

124
00:06:09,821 --> 00:06:10,741
are possible?

125
00:06:21,181 --> 00:06:21,980
Auntie,

126
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:23,660
Wanqing is here.

127
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:25,780
I brought you a small gift.

128
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:27,980
Hope you like it.

129
00:06:28,421 --> 00:06:29,821
It's so beautiful.

130
00:06:30,261 --> 00:06:31,100
Wanqing,

131
00:06:31,621 --> 00:06:33,181
you are so kind.

132
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:34,220
Auntie,

133
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:35,941
you always take care of me,

134
00:06:36,421 --> 00:06:38,020
it's my pleasure to do something for you.

135
00:06:39,061 --> 00:06:40,061
Wanqing,

136
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:42,501
I really like you more and more,

137
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:45,301
I wish you could marry my son earlier.

138
00:06:47,861 --> 00:06:48,741
Auntie,

139
00:06:49,741 --> 00:06:50,821
I just don't know

140
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,540
which one to marry.

141
00:07:05,941 --> 00:07:06,741
Madam,

142
00:07:06,980 --> 00:07:08,020
what are you doing here?

143
00:07:10,821 --> 00:07:11,941
Can't I be here?

144
00:07:12,861 --> 00:07:13,660
No, Madam,

145
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:14,460
I didn't mean that.

146
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:15,261
What are you doing?

147
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,381
I just told Young Master Yan...

148
00:07:16,381 --> 00:07:18,181
Why are you dressed like this?

149
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:20,301
Do you really think you're the lady of the house?

150
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:22,261
Wanting to marry into a rich family, huh?

151
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:24,301
The Gu family has its rules.

152
00:07:24,741 --> 00:07:25,941
Everyone except the Gu family

153
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:28,181
must wear uniform clothing.

154
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,501
Didn't anyone tell you that?

155
00:07:30,501 --> 00:07:31,100
Madam, you've got it wrong.

156
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:32,100
Enough, stop talking.

157
00:07:33,181 --> 00:07:35,540
Don't ever dress me in these clothes again.

158
00:07:36,621 --> 00:07:38,020
Change your clothes now.

159
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,261
and clean the backyard.

160
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:55,621
Madam, I'll clean the yard.

161
00:07:56,301 --> 00:07:57,020
Go.

162
00:07:57,460 --> 00:07:58,220
Okay.

163
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,701
The theme of our exhibition

164
00:08:19,340 --> 00:08:20,261
is innovation,

165
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:21,381
cooperation,

166
00:08:21,861 --> 00:08:22,540
excellence,

167
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,941
promoting communication among employees,

168
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:26,261
and team spirit.

169
00:08:40,301 --> 00:08:41,141
Take a look for yourself.

170
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,021
What have you done?

171
00:08:43,260 --> 00:08:44,541
This is how you treat clients?

172
00:08:51,301 --> 00:08:52,901
Be careful, don't break it.

173
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:04,500
Madam, I've finished cleaning.

174
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:05,421
The pool...
